# Conductors and Insulators

![](data:image/gif;base64,)

There are three types of materials: [Conductor](20220408103508-conductor.md), [Semiconductor](20220225130808-semiconductor.md), and [Insulator](20220408103758-insulator.md).

The material determines the [Resistance](Resistance) of the object.
